<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA36">
<l>maṟuvuṭaiya kaṇṭattīr vārcaṭaimē ṉākan</l>
<l>teṟumeṉṟu tēyntuḻalu māvā - vuṟuvāṉ</l>
<l>ṟaḷaramī tōṭumē ṟāṉataṉai yañci</l>
<l>vaḷarumō piḷḷai mati</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with a stained throat, it wanders, diminishing at the thought</l>
<l>“the snake on [you] long matted locks will torment [me].” Oh-oh, fearing it,</l>
<l>when it runs upon it, when it is feeble, in order to have it,</l>
<l>will it grow, the child moon?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
